      ],
      "notes": "<p>A small Digimon with four limbs extending from underneath its body (head?). These limbs, which are highly unusual on an In-Training Digimon, give Tokomon a unique and extremely cute look. However, that cuteness can be deceptive, and anyone who reaches out to pet Tokomon may be in for a surprise as it quickly opens its mouth and bites down with its rows of sharp teeth. Tokomon has an innocent personality, though, and doesn’t mean any real harm.</p>"
